Name: MethodOfAdministration
Description: Describes the method of pretest administration using a controlled vocabulary and description.

Name: ModeOfPretestCollection
Description: Describes the mode of collection used in the pretest. Repeat of multiple modes of collection were used. Indicate the primary mode using isPrimary attribute if applicable.

Name: AdditionalDataCollection
Description: Description of the method and mode of data collection in administering the pretest. Notes any additional data collected in the administration of the pretest.
